tradingagents.dataflows.get_finnhub_news(ticker: Annotated[str, "Search query of a company's, e.g. 'AAPL, TSM, etc."], curr_date: Annotated[str, 'Current date in yyyy-mm-dd format'], look_back_days: Annotated[int, 'how many days to look back'])[source]

Retrieve news about a company within a time frame

Args

ticker (str): ticker for the company you are interested in start_date (str): Start date in yyyy-mm-dd format end_date (str): End date in yyyy-mm-dd format

Returns

str: dataframe containing the news of the company in the time frame

tradingagents.dataflows.get_finnhub_company_insider_sentiment(ticker: Annotated[str, 'ticker symbol for the company'], curr_date: Annotated[str, 'current date of you are trading at, yyyy-mm-dd'], look_back_days: Annotated[int, 'number of days to look back'])[source]

Retrieve insider sentiment about a company (retrieved from public SEC information) for the past 15 days :param ticker: ticker symbol of the company :type ticker: str :param curr_date: current date you are trading on, yyyy-mm-dd :type curr_date: str

Returns:

a report of the sentiment in the past 15 days starting at curr_date

Return type:

str
